sections.text:
72-806.Enforcement.

The enforcement provisions of Chapter 1 of the 2018 International Energy Conservation Code, published by the International Code Council, shall not apply to buildings subject to section 72-804.

SourceLaws 1999, LB 755, § 3;Laws 2003, LB 643, § 4;Laws 2004, LB 888, § 3;Laws 2011, LB329, § 3;Laws 2019, LB405, § 5.
